channel.title: In need of a server sided coder!
channel.description:
I have to much to fix that i don't know where to start and let alone how to do some of it. Im looking for a coder who has experience in coding 562 rs2hd based servers, that just want to code.
I will give you all the credit you deserve please let me know if you are interested.
Please post your experience and work?
The site i hope to have someone helping me on is right here. We only have about 10 actives because i put it up yesterday night. [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php?server=darkscapeeee.no-ip.biz]http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php?server=darkscapeeee.no-ip.biz[/url]
